'''Telugu Saamskruthika Niketanam''' is all so called as '''World Telugu Museum''' is located in [[Visakhapatnam]], [[Andhra Pradesh]],[[India]]. it was established in the year of 2015 by [[Andhra Pradesh]] Chief Minister [[N. Chandrababu Naidu]].<ref>http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Visakhapatnam/cm-to-open-telugu-heritage-museum/</ref>
==Objectives== The main objective of this museum is to elaborate Telugu history and culture from [[Satavahana dynasty]] to till now.the Telugu museum is showing 42 episodes of Telugu culture, arts,folk arts, great poets,language, literature and history of great personalities in Telugu society.<ref>http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/hyderabad/Telugu-museum-to-open-in-Vizag-soon/articleshow/17564245.cms</ref>
